 975:lib/tinyusb/src/common/tusb_fifo.c **** /*!
 976:lib/tinyusb/src/common/tusb_fifo.c ****    @brief Get read info
 977:lib/tinyusb/src/common/tusb_fifo.c **** 
 978:lib/tinyusb/src/common/tusb_fifo.c ****    Returns the length and pointer from which bytes can be read in a linear manner.
 979:lib/tinyusb/src/common/tusb_fifo.c ****    This is of major interest for DMA transmissions. If returned length is zero the
